1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 18 =

20
00:01:40,340 --> 00:01:41,620
Which one is better,

21
00:01:41,700 --> 00:01:43,100
Lv Yijian or Fan Zhongyan?

22
00:01:47,500 --> 00:01:49,060
I’m too ignorant to judge.

23
00:01:52,860 --> 00:01:54,180
You were always with me

24
00:01:54,300 --> 00:01:55,540
when I learned from teachers

25
00:01:55,660 --> 00:01:57,260
and the Empress Dowager.

26
00:01:57,740 --> 00:01:58,780
When at court,

27
00:01:58,780 --> 00:02:00,820
you’ve witnessed officials’ arguments.

28
00:02:01,380 --> 00:02:02,580
How could you be ignorant?

29
00:02:04,380 --> 00:02:06,900
I dare not comment on state business.

30
00:02:10,260 --> 00:02:12,340
You only comment on Danshu

31
00:02:14,300 --> 00:02:15,100
and…

32
00:02:15,540 --> 00:02:17,340
and other concubines.

33
00:02:24,780 --> 00:02:26,380
Even you’ve become more restrained.

34
00:02:26,780 --> 00:02:28,220
How boring!

35
00:02:29,260 --> 00:02:29,940
Never mind.

36
00:02:59,500 --> 00:03:00,500
Maoze,

37
00:03:03,460 --> 00:03:04,460
you’ve gained

38
00:03:05,460 --> 00:03:07,700
more power over the years.

39
00:03:09,460 --> 00:03:10,420
Is your life

40
00:03:11,060 --> 00:03:12,500
easier than before?

41
00:03:17,140 --> 00:03:18,260
My current post

42
00:03:18,500 --> 00:03:20,140
allows me to leave the palace more easily.

43
00:03:20,660 --> 00:03:22,220
If there are snacks

44
00:03:22,220 --> 00:03:22,980
or playthings you want,

45
00:03:23,740 --> 00:03:25,060
I can purchase them for you.

46
00:03:27,900 --> 00:03:28,900
In the past,

47
00:03:30,500 --> 00:03:32,100
we asked people we trusted

48
00:03:32,100 --> 00:03:34,900
to buy snacks and toys for us

49
00:03:36,020 --> 00:03:38,180
and tell us folk tales

50
00:03:39,460 --> 00:03:41,820
behind the Empress Dowager’s back.

51
00:03:42,660 --> 00:03:44,140
And I had to be always prepared

52
00:03:44,300 --> 00:03:48,180
for her tests on knowledge, politics

53
00:03:48,580 --> 00:03:49,580
or etiquettes.

54
00:03:51,260 --> 00:03:52,140
Back then,

55
00:03:52,700 --> 00:03:55,540
I couldn’t wait for her to go to the temple.

56
00:03:57,780 --> 00:03:59,380
Every time before she left,

57
00:03:59,860 --> 00:04:01,740
you’d make plans with me in advance

58
00:04:01,780 --> 00:04:03,060
about what we would do.

59
00:04:03,900 --> 00:04:04,820
One time,

60
00:04:05,660 --> 00:04:07,540
when she was about to be away for a month,

61
00:04:07,900 --> 00:04:09,660
we chatted for a whole night,

62
00:04:09,860 --> 00:04:10,580
yet...

63
00:04:11,420 --> 00:04:12,980
yet you caught a cold

64
00:04:13,180 --> 00:04:14,500
and fell ill the next day.

65
00:04:15,020 --> 00:04:16,060
She was worried

66
00:04:16,500 --> 00:04:18,300
and canceled her trip.

67
00:04:22,260 --> 00:04:24,060
When Mr. Yan came to visit me,

68
00:04:24,820 --> 00:04:25,860
he said to her that

69
00:04:26,940 --> 00:04:28,340
I was too ill

70
00:04:29,300 --> 00:04:30,820
to read or write.

71
00:04:31,780 --> 00:04:33,900
He could tell me stories in the book.

72
00:04:35,580 --> 00:04:36,100
Then he picked one

73
00:04:36,100 --> 00:04:37,420
in Records of the Grand Historian on purpose,

74
00:04:37,820 --> 00:04:40,900
about Chunyu Kun dissuading King Wei of Qi

75
00:04:40,900 --> 00:04:42,660
from holding evening banquets.

76
00:04:44,020 --> 00:04:46,700
In the end, Chunyu said,

77
00:04:47,340 --> 00:04:49,700
“Drunkenness induces misconduct;
extreme joy begets sorrow.

78
00:04:50,300 --> 00:04:51,460
So is everything else”.

79
00:04:52,580 --> 00:04:54,500
When he said “extreme joy begets sorrow”,

80
00:04:54,500 --> 00:04:55,860
he smiled at me.

81
00:04:56,860 --> 00:04:58,100
I looked over his shoulder

82
00:04:58,780 --> 00:05:00,660
and saw the Empress Dowager

83
00:05:00,660 --> 00:05:02,220
reviewing proposals while looking after me.

84
00:05:03,820 --> 00:05:05,420
Then I thanked him sincerely

85
00:05:05,580 --> 00:05:07,020
for his instruction

86
00:05:07,820 --> 00:05:11,140
and admired the predecessors’ wisdom.

87
00:05:19,300 --> 00:05:20,700
After the Empress Dowager passed away,

88
00:05:22,500 --> 00:05:24,620
I didn’t feel relaxed, though.

89
00:05:27,180 --> 00:05:28,900
People and things I have to guard against

90
00:05:30,660 --> 00:05:31,580
increased tenfold,

91
00:05:33,220 --> 00:05:34,100
hundredfold,

92
00:05:36,340 --> 00:05:37,220
thousandfold.

93
00:06:10,460 --> 00:06:11,460
The Scholar Academy

94
00:06:11,460 --> 00:06:12,540
has issued the appointment announcement.

95
00:06:12,900 --> 00:06:14,420
Zhang Shixun is appointed Minister of Scholar;

96
00:06:14,460 --> 00:06:16,380
Zhang Dexiang, Minister of Talent.

97
00:06:16,660 --> 00:06:17,780
Quite unexpected.

98
00:06:19,180 --> 00:06:20,300
I heard

99
00:06:20,460 --> 00:06:21,460
after the four ministers were dismissed,

100
00:06:21,780 --> 00:06:23,220
the most possible candidates to replace them

101
00:06:23,220 --> 00:06:24,620
were Fan Zhongyan, Xu Yan,

102
00:06:25,220 --> 00:06:26,220
and

103
00:06:26,420 --> 00:06:28,780
Wang Zeng, Lv Yijian, Song Shou.

104
00:06:29,260 --> 00:06:31,460
Some nominated Yan Shu and Du Yan,

105
00:06:31,780 --> 00:06:33,380
but those two officials were appointed.

106
00:06:35,300 --> 00:06:36,340
Did you hear anything

107
00:06:36,380 --> 00:06:37,860
at the Scholar Academy?

108
00:06:39,860 --> 00:06:40,620
Nothing.

109
00:06:42,020 --> 00:06:43,380
I share everything with you.

110
00:06:43,780 --> 00:06:45,100
How could you hide things from me?

111
00:06:45,380 --> 00:06:46,700
Su Shunqin and Cai Xiang

112
00:06:46,700 --> 00:06:47,980
are big-mouthed.

113
00:06:48,180 --> 00:06:49,580
How could they say nothing about it?

114
00:06:51,500 --> 00:06:54,660
= Liang Huaiji =
Scholar Su was assigned to draft up the decree

115
00:06:54,660 --> 00:06:56,300
to confer the title of Fukang on Princess.

116
00:06:57,300 --> 00:06:58,860
His Majesty reviewed it

117
00:06:59,260 --> 00:07:01,700
and was dissatisfied with a few words.

118
00:07:02,540 --> 00:07:04,780
= Zhang Chengzhao =

119
00:07:04,780 --> 00:07:06,500
Then Scholar Su went to the library

120
00:07:06,620 --> 00:07:07,980
to look up old records.

121
00:07:08,180 --> 00:07:09,620
Censor Han was summoned

122
00:07:09,820 --> 00:07:11,620
to the Hall of Politics early this morning.

123
00:07:11,700 --> 00:07:12,940
Summoned to the Hall of Politics?

124
00:07:13,300 --> 00:07:14,220
Who else went there?

125
00:07:15,380 --> 00:07:16,300
I don’t know.

126
00:07:21,460 --> 00:07:23,260
Shixun used to teach me

127
00:07:23,660 --> 00:07:25,420
at the Eastern Palace.

128
00:07:25,660 --> 00:07:26,780
He’s virtuous and knowledgeable.

129
00:07:27,060 --> 00:07:28,380
I’m deeply impressed.

130
00:07:30,100 --> 00:07:33,180
Dexiang has always been down to earth

131
00:07:34,060 --> 00:07:35,820
and never sided with others.

132
00:07:36,020 --> 00:07:36,980
A few days ago,

133
00:07:37,380 --> 00:07:38,380
Lv Yijian wrote

134
00:07:38,540 --> 00:07:40,140
a 10,000-word long letter to my father-in-law

135
00:07:40,380 --> 00:07:41,740
about the situation in the west.

136
00:07:42,660 --> 00:07:44,100
My father-in-law

137
00:07:44,100 --> 00:07:45,180
agreed to a few things he mentioned,

138
00:07:45,820 --> 00:07:46,580
such as

139
00:07:47,100 --> 00:07:49,740
the west is a valley-land and sparsely populated.

140
00:07:49,900 --> 00:07:51,620
There are no natural barriers.

141
00:07:52,460 --> 00:07:54,260
The Tanguts are fierce in nature

142
00:07:54,540 --> 00:07:56,060
and always raid in small groups.

143
00:07:56,580 --> 00:07:57,820
We should build forts

144
00:07:57,820 --> 00:08:00,140
along the valley where most people reside

145
00:08:00,380 --> 00:08:01,100
and have them guarded.

146
00:08:01,100 --> 00:08:01,860
Talents are needed at this moment.

147
00:08:02,460 --> 00:08:03,700
After careful consideration,

148
00:08:04,860 --> 00:08:05,940
the state still needs

149
00:08:06,340 --> 00:08:07,820
your services.

150
00:08:11,700 --> 00:08:12,900
Thank you for Your Majesty’s appreciation.

151
00:08:13,100 --> 00:08:14,620
We’ll give it our all

152
00:08:14,860 --> 00:08:16,180
till the end.

153
00:08:16,860 --> 00:08:17,820
Please be seated.

154
00:08:18,260 --> 00:08:19,420
Thank you, Your Majesty.

155
00:08:28,100 --> 00:08:29,700
I’d like to consult you

156
00:08:30,060 --> 00:08:31,660
about the situation in the west.

157
00:08:35,580 --> 00:08:37,740
Zhao Yuanhao didn’t pay tribute on time.

158
00:08:37,980 --> 00:08:40,700
= Zhang Shixun, courtesy name Shunzhi =
We should condemn him

159
00:08:41,060 --> 00:08:43,580
and educate him with our rules and manners

160
00:08:43,900 --> 00:08:44,860
to change him.

161
00:08:47,540 --> 00:08:48,300
Your Majesty,

162
00:08:48,900 --> 00:08:50,380
I have disagreements.

163
00:08:50,980 --> 00:08:51,900
You may speak, Han Qi.

164
00:08:53,540 --> 00:08:54,380
In my opinion,

165
00:08:54,660 --> 00:08:56,500
Yuanhao is as violent, unruly and cunning

166
00:08:56,660 --> 00:08:58,700
as his father and grandfather.

167
00:08:58,700 --> 00:08:59,700
He can’t be trusted

168
00:08:59,860 --> 00:09:02,020
or changed by words or manners.

169
00:09:02,660 --> 00:09:03,260
To date,

170
00:09:03,260 --> 00:09:05,380
he’s defeated Tibet and Uighur

171
00:09:05,420 --> 00:09:07,220
and quashed the internal strife,

172
00:09:07,300 --> 00:09:08,660
and he definitely wants more.

173
00:09:09,100 --> 00:09:10,820
It’s possible

174
00:09:10,980 --> 00:09:12,420
that he’ll invade us.

175
00:09:19,580 --> 00:09:23,020
= Yan Mansion =

176
00:09:27,380 --> 00:09:28,820
Postponing Lv Yijian’s reinstatement

177
00:09:29,100 --> 00:09:29,980
is wise.

178
00:09:30,420 --> 00:09:31,380
He only got demoted not long ago.

179
00:09:32,300 --> 00:09:33,380
If he were called back

180
00:09:33,580 --> 00:09:34,660
when the disaster rises,

181
00:09:37,020 --> 00:09:38,740
others might think

182
00:09:38,900 --> 00:09:39,980
the state couldn’t survive without him.

183
00:09:41,300 --> 00:09:41,940
But

184
00:09:42,220 --> 00:09:44,260
there are better candidates

185
00:09:44,620 --> 00:09:46,700
than Zhang Dexiang and Zhang Shixun.

186
00:09:47,380 --> 00:09:50,140
Fan Zhongyan was honest and blunt

187
00:09:50,900 --> 00:09:51,860
when giving advice in the Capital.

188
00:09:52,340 --> 00:09:53,460
As the local governor,

189
00:09:53,580 --> 00:09:54,740
he was organized

190
00:09:54,740 --> 00:09:56,020
and responsible.

191
00:09:56,100 --> 00:09:57,580
The locals respected him highly.

192
00:09:58,060 --> 00:09:58,820
Back then,

193
00:09:59,420 --> 00:10:00,820
he was restricted by Lv Yijian.

194
00:10:01,260 --> 00:10:03,220
Why can’t he be recalled

195
00:10:03,220 --> 00:10:04,180
and promoted?

196
00:10:04,220 --> 00:10:05,420
He’s the ideal person.

197
00:10:06,980 --> 00:10:09,300
Too ideal, I’m afraid.

198
00:10:14,620 --> 00:10:15,860
Xiwen is noble

199
00:10:16,900 --> 00:10:19,180
and regarded as the spiritual leader

200
00:10:20,260 --> 00:10:21,300
simply because of his virtues.

201
00:10:21,820 --> 00:10:24,740
Is His Majesty afraid of his influence?

202
00:10:27,220 --> 00:10:28,380
If there’s one person

203
00:10:28,980 --> 00:10:31,580
who’s admired and respected by all

204
00:10:31,900 --> 00:10:33,140
and can lead

205
00:10:33,140 --> 00:10:35,100
the scholars to be dedicated,

206
00:10:35,380 --> 00:10:36,780
eventually,

207
00:10:36,900 --> 00:10:38,260
the new trend

208
00:10:38,260 --> 00:10:39,780
will replace the old.

209
00:10:40,260 --> 00:10:41,260
Isn’t he a rare talent?

210
00:10:41,700 --> 00:10:43,940
There’s no need to put him over the fire.

211
00:10:47,380 --> 00:10:48,620
Over the fire?

212
00:10:51,020 --> 00:10:52,700
If he becomes the Prime Minister

213
00:10:53,460 --> 00:10:54,500
and takes charge of state affairs,

214
00:10:54,700 --> 00:10:56,540
he’ll face His Majesty, officials and the public.

215
00:10:57,500 --> 00:11:00,780
Not only will he have to give advice,

216
00:11:01,180 --> 00:11:03,020
but he’ll also have to bear the consequence

217
00:11:03,700 --> 00:11:04,820
and handle the aftermath.

218
00:11:05,780 --> 00:11:06,900
His concerns

219
00:11:07,060 --> 00:11:08,180
and compromises

220
00:11:09,340 --> 00:11:10,740
will concern the entire state.

221
00:11:11,220 --> 00:11:12,300
Rules he has to follow

222
00:11:13,620 --> 00:11:16,140
aren’t just those of scholars.

223
00:11:17,700 --> 00:11:18,940
Aren’t Confucius and Mencius sages?

224
00:11:19,580 --> 00:11:20,300
Did they

225
00:11:20,980 --> 00:11:22,780
have important posts

226
00:11:23,220 --> 00:11:24,820
or huge power

227
00:11:25,820 --> 00:11:28,740
or did they ever control state affairs?

228
00:11:38,820 --> 00:11:40,260
Did you learn valuable advice

229
00:11:40,660 --> 00:11:42,980
when meeting His Majesty with new ministers?

230
00:11:46,580 --> 00:11:48,700
Educate Yuanhao with our rules and manners

231
00:11:48,980 --> 00:11:49,780
= Su Shunqin, courtesy name Zimei =
to change his violent nature

232
00:11:50,180 --> 00:11:51,860
so that he’ll be disciplined and mannered.

233
00:11:54,220 --> 00:11:55,300
I have a proposal.

234
00:11:55,900 --> 00:11:57,100
We should deliver books to Xixia.

235
00:11:57,580 --> 00:11:58,740
That’s not enough, of course.

236
00:11:59,420 --> 00:12:00,500
A barbarian like Yuanhao

237
00:12:00,860 --> 00:12:02,340
is unable to read between the lines.

238
00:12:02,700 --> 00:12:05,220
We should assign an erudite scholar

239
00:12:05,540 --> 00:12:06,580
to teach him.

240
00:12:08,500 --> 00:12:09,580
Minister Zhang is a master

241
00:12:09,740 --> 00:12:11,700
and fits to be the envoy.

242
00:12:15,540 --> 00:12:16,580
Later on,

243
00:12:16,780 --> 00:12:19,660
His Majesty asked our opinions about the west.

244
00:12:20,620 --> 00:12:22,140
Xia Song and Li Ruogu

245
00:12:22,460 --> 00:12:23,540
are always sophisticated.

246
00:12:23,820 --> 00:12:24,900
Their speeches

247
00:12:25,460 --> 00:12:26,860
are a bunch of nonsense.

248
00:12:27,380 --> 00:12:29,580
Only I expressed concerns.

249
00:12:30,220 --> 00:12:31,220
What did His Majesty say?

250
00:12:32,900 --> 00:12:33,660
I guess he said,

251
00:12:36,860 --> 00:12:38,140
“All your opinions

252
00:12:38,340 --> 00:12:40,820
are worth consideration”.

253
00:12:44,180 --> 00:12:45,100
I think

254
00:12:45,660 --> 00:12:47,620
His Majesty knows well

255
00:12:47,820 --> 00:12:49,020
about the west.

256
00:12:50,100 --> 00:12:51,700
Problem is our traditional system

257
00:12:51,780 --> 00:12:52,860
only focuses on internal defense.

258
00:12:53,100 --> 00:12:54,340
Liao is on the north

259
00:12:54,620 --> 00:12:55,940
facing no barriers.

260
00:12:56,780 --> 00:12:58,060
Without conquering the west,

261
00:12:58,380 --> 00:12:59,820
we can’t get fine horses.

262
00:13:01,660 --> 00:13:02,780
Waging war is doable

263
00:13:03,900 --> 00:13:05,140
but not the wisest.

264
00:13:25,580 --> 00:13:26,580
In 1004 A.D.,

265
00:13:27,380 --> 00:13:29,660
when Li Jiqian died of injury,

266
00:13:29,940 --> 00:13:31,180
the Tanguts were battling for power.

267
00:13:31,380 --> 00:13:33,380
Major tribes in the west didn’t support Li Deming.

268
00:13:33,420 --> 00:13:34,220
Tibet and the others

269
00:13:34,220 --> 00:13:35,780
were eager to occupy their land.

270
00:13:35,980 --> 00:13:38,260
General Cao Wei

271
00:13:38,260 --> 00:13:39,940
begged the late Emperor repeatedly

272
00:13:39,940 --> 00:13:41,140
to ally with Tibet

273
00:13:41,140 --> 00:13:42,100
to eliminate the Tanguts,

274
00:13:42,100 --> 00:13:43,660
making the west our county

275
00:13:43,660 --> 00:13:44,940
to end the struggle once and for all.

276
00:13:48,420 --> 00:13:49,220
Unfortunately,

277
00:13:50,580 --> 00:13:51,820
the late Emperor said

278
00:13:51,900 --> 00:13:53,700
“unlike his father, Deming was loyal”

279
00:13:53,700 --> 00:13:54,780
and denied General Cao’s request.

280
00:13:55,100 --> 00:13:56,100
One misjudgment in the past

281
00:13:56,100 --> 00:13:57,140
leads to a huge disaster.

282
00:13:57,340 --> 00:13:58,540
If we repeat that mistake,

283
00:13:58,540 --> 00:13:59,820
our state will...

284
00:14:20,820 --> 00:14:21,900
Men are supposed to

285
00:14:22,860 --> 00:14:24,860
fight on the battlefield

286
00:14:25,220 --> 00:14:27,140
and safeguard the nation with our lives.

287
00:14:27,980 --> 00:14:28,740
Yet here I am

288
00:14:29,340 --> 00:14:30,420
pondering over words

289
00:14:30,580 --> 00:14:31,740
for a decree of conferring the title

290
00:14:31,740 --> 00:14:34,260
of Fukang on a less than one-year-old princess.

291
00:14:34,900 --> 00:14:36,220
There’s a fixed format

292
00:14:36,220 --> 00:14:37,060
for this kind of decree,

293
00:14:37,580 --> 00:14:39,740
but His Majesty read and edited it twice.

294
00:14:40,300 --> 00:14:42,180
She won’t be the Crown Prince.

295
00:14:42,180 --> 00:14:43,260
However noble she is,

296
00:14:43,260 --> 00:14:44,460
all her children

297
00:14:44,460 --> 00:14:45,740
will be named after another man.

298
00:14:45,740 --> 00:14:46,460
Zimei,

299
00:14:47,500 --> 00:14:48,380
watch your language.

300
00:15:03,220 --> 00:15:04,340
His Majesty has all kinds of virtues,

301
00:15:06,300 --> 00:15:07,860
but he can be indecisive

302
00:15:09,060 --> 00:15:10,460
and soft-hearted sometimes.

303
00:15:16,860 --> 00:15:21,660
= Yanzhou (today Yan’an) =

304
00:15:23,220 --> 00:15:23,820
Come on.

305
00:15:26,380 --> 00:15:27,300
Hurry! Hurry up!

306
00:15:30,220 --> 00:15:31,620
We’re back full-handed!

307
00:15:40,540 --> 00:15:41,300
Mr. Di.

308
00:15:41,940 --> 00:15:43,300
You came at the right time.

309
00:15:43,820 --> 00:15:44,940
You went over there to exchange tea bricks

310
00:15:45,700 --> 00:15:48,460
for salt and meat again?

311
00:15:49,340 --> 00:15:49,940
Yes.

312
00:15:50,020 --> 00:15:50,820
Look,

313
00:15:50,940 --> 00:15:52,740
the sheep are big.

314
00:15:52,860 --> 00:15:53,620
I’ll have them

315
00:15:53,620 --> 00:15:54,500
boiled later.

316
00:15:54,820 --> 00:15:55,740
We can have

317
00:15:55,940 --> 00:15:57,220
a big meal tomorrow.

318
00:15:58,460 --> 00:15:59,260
From now on,

319
00:15:59,740 --> 00:16:01,100
nobody is allowed

320
00:16:01,100 --> 00:16:02,060
to see those people again.

321
00:16:02,780 --> 00:16:04,460
= Di Qing, courtesy name Hanchen =
Or you’ll commit treason.

322
00:16:10,100 --> 00:16:12,140
You won’t be punished today.

323
00:16:13,180 --> 00:16:14,180
= Liang Yuansheng =
I mean

324
00:16:15,260 --> 00:16:16,300
you can no longer

325
00:16:17,180 --> 00:16:18,700
trade with them.

326
00:16:21,740 --> 00:16:23,180
So Zhao Yuanhao’s really crowned himself.

327
00:16:23,740 --> 00:16:24,420
Liang Yuansheng,

328
00:16:25,260 --> 00:16:26,660
Mr. Di is speaking.

329
00:16:26,660 --> 00:16:27,580
Don’t interrupt him.

330
00:16:28,100 --> 00:16:29,180
What I said is true.

331
00:16:29,980 --> 00:16:31,980
Zhao Yuanhao discarded his surname

332
00:16:32,420 --> 00:16:33,780
and renamed himself Nangxiao.

333
00:16:34,340 --> 00:16:35,380
He also calls himself Wuzu,

334
00:16:35,820 --> 00:16:37,180
meaning emperor.

335
00:16:37,540 --> 00:16:38,500
Five days ago,

336
00:16:38,580 --> 00:16:40,100
a ceremony was held to pay respects to heaven.

337
00:16:48,380 --> 00:16:49,380
Just now, I heard from them

338
00:16:50,140 --> 00:16:52,580
that they’ve become the people of Xixia

339
00:16:53,100 --> 00:16:54,140
and have to call Zhao Yuanhao Wuzu.

340
00:16:54,140 --> 00:16:55,260
He has a new name now.

341
00:16:55,860 --> 00:16:57,500
I saw the announcements on the wall

342
00:16:58,660 --> 00:17:00,100
and took one when no one was looking.

343
00:17:00,660 --> 00:17:02,020
Can you understand their language

344
00:17:02,540 --> 00:17:03,500
and read their words?

345
00:17:04,140 --> 00:17:06,180
I can understand them well

346
00:17:06,540 --> 00:17:07,740
but I only recognize words

347
00:17:08,500 --> 00:17:10,460
about trade and business.

348
00:17:13,820 --> 00:17:14,580
Follow me.

349
00:18:00,300 --> 00:18:00,980
Princess.

350
00:18:01,100 --> 00:18:02,340
She enjoys a big crowd.

351
00:18:03,260 --> 00:18:05,060
The more people she sees,

352
00:18:05,140 --> 00:18:06,860
the happier she becomes.

353
00:18:07,820 --> 00:18:08,860
Since I told her earlier

354
00:18:09,220 --> 00:18:11,980
that her father would take her to the banquet

355
00:18:12,620 --> 00:18:14,220
to see beautiful girls

356
00:18:14,220 --> 00:18:16,060
play the instruments and dance,

357
00:18:16,580 --> 00:18:18,140
I’m not sure whether she understood it

358
00:18:18,140 --> 00:18:19,100
or not,

359
00:18:19,540 --> 00:18:21,660
she’s been happy the whole day.

360
00:18:23,340 --> 00:18:24,540
Princess is beauty-conscious, too.

361
00:18:24,740 --> 00:18:25,660
When she heard

362
00:18:25,660 --> 00:18:26,940
there would be beautiful girls dancing,

363
00:18:26,980 --> 00:18:28,740
she grabbed Madam Miao’s blusher and accessories

364
00:18:28,740 --> 00:18:29,740
and refused to let go of them.

365
00:18:29,980 --> 00:18:31,220
That’s right.

366
00:18:31,540 --> 00:18:32,900
She didn’t drop the blusher

367
00:18:32,900 --> 00:18:34,220
until being dressed up.

368
00:18:35,140 --> 00:18:35,860
Your Majesty.

369
00:18:38,820 --> 00:18:39,900
Even without makeup,

370
00:18:40,580 --> 00:18:41,860
my daughter Huirou

371
00:18:42,140 --> 00:18:44,100
is still the fairest in the world.

372
00:18:44,820 --> 00:18:45,900
No one is her match.

373
00:18:55,900 --> 00:18:57,420
Rest assured, Deputy Officer Yang.

374
00:18:57,620 --> 00:18:59,220
Everything is set.

375
00:19:00,220 --> 00:19:02,220
After a month of intense practice,

376
00:19:02,580 --> 00:19:03,700
those girls can finally perform

377
00:19:03,700 --> 00:19:04,980
in front of His Majesty, Her Highness

378
00:19:05,140 --> 00:19:06,660
as well as other members

379
00:19:06,660 --> 00:19:07,300
of the royal family.

380
00:19:07,660 --> 00:19:09,980
They’re all excited.

381
00:19:11,660 --> 00:19:13,500
Alright. Stop chatting.

382
00:19:13,620 --> 00:19:14,900
Go get ready.

383
00:19:15,380 --> 00:19:16,420
- Yes. - Yes.

384
00:19:16,540 --> 00:19:18,060
- Let’s go. - Let’s go back.

385
00:19:25,660 --> 00:19:27,460
The list has been submitted.

386
00:19:28,780 --> 00:19:30,300
When I help His Majesty get changed

387
00:19:30,300 --> 00:19:32,340
before the banquet,

388
00:19:32,500 --> 00:19:33,700
I’ll tell him

389
00:19:33,740 --> 00:19:36,420
that you’ve agreed to the betrothal for Bihan,

390
00:19:36,620 --> 00:19:38,220
and she’s going on a hunger strike

391
00:19:38,340 --> 00:19:40,220
for replacing her with another dancer today.

392
00:19:43,540 --> 00:19:44,300
That girl

393
00:19:44,860 --> 00:19:46,300
is tough as nails.

394
00:19:47,660 --> 00:19:49,060
She’s determined

395
00:19:49,380 --> 00:19:50,460
to marry His Majesty,

396
00:19:51,900 --> 00:19:53,020
or she’d rather die.

397
00:19:56,100 --> 00:19:57,860
You’re too partial to her.

398
00:19:58,340 --> 00:19:59,820
Lantiao

399
00:19:59,820 --> 00:20:00,460
is as charming as her

400
00:20:00,460 --> 00:20:01,860
after she’s dressed up.

401
00:20:02,140 --> 00:20:04,660
Besides, she’s much more tender.

402
00:20:05,380 --> 00:20:07,140
After the dance, His Majesty may find her

403
00:20:08,460 --> 00:20:09,460
more attractive.

404
00:20:14,300 --> 00:20:15,300
Bihan,

405
00:20:15,820 --> 00:20:17,540
you haven’t eaten for three days.

406
00:20:18,180 --> 00:20:19,700
You’ll collapse.

407
00:20:21,940 --> 00:20:23,100
Stop doing this.

408
00:20:23,540 --> 00:20:25,260
They’ve left for the banquet.

409
00:20:26,340 --> 00:20:28,220
Lantiao will perform your dance

410
00:20:28,740 --> 00:20:30,260
and have the chance to shine.

411
00:20:54,180 --> 00:20:56,220
Merciful Buddha, Jade Emperor,

412
00:20:57,660 --> 00:20:58,740
listen,

413
00:21:02,100 --> 00:21:02,900
I,

414
00:21:04,220 --> 00:21:05,220
Zhang Bihan,

415
00:21:07,340 --> 00:21:09,300
am willing to sacrifice half of my life

416
00:21:10,940 --> 00:21:12,260
just for His Majesty

417
00:21:12,900 --> 00:21:14,940
won’t pay attention to that tramp

418
00:21:16,100 --> 00:21:17,380
who performs my dance in my dress.

419
00:21:30,940 --> 00:21:32,220
Hold the gate!

420
00:21:33,820 --> 00:21:34,500
Open it.

421
00:21:41,060 --> 00:21:43,860
= Privy Council =

422
00:21:46,380 --> 00:21:47,580
What’s going on?

423
00:21:48,100 --> 00:21:49,140
= Xia Song, courtesy name Ziqiao =
What’s with the rush?

424
00:21:49,340 --> 00:21:50,420
Military or disaster report?

425
00:21:50,540 --> 00:21:51,380
The west.

426
00:21:51,380 --> 00:21:52,020
West...

427
00:22:15,260 --> 00:22:16,100
How did it go?

428
00:22:16,620 --> 00:22:18,380
Not good.

429
00:22:18,860 --> 00:22:19,540
What’s wrong?

430
00:22:20,660 --> 00:22:22,580
His Majesty went to the Pavilion of Phoenix

431
00:22:22,580 --> 00:22:23,460
to get changed.

432
00:22:23,460 --> 00:22:24,420
I waited here

433
00:22:24,420 --> 00:22:26,140
for a chance to talk to him after he arrived.

434
00:22:26,660 --> 00:22:28,380
But just now, Zhang Maoze said

435
00:22:28,380 --> 00:22:30,140
the Cabinet handed in an urgent proposal

436
00:22:30,140 --> 00:22:31,660
and asked to see His Majesty.

437
00:22:32,620 --> 00:22:33,660
What happened?

438
00:22:35,620 --> 00:22:37,380
There’s no chance

439
00:22:37,380 --> 00:22:38,420
to talk to him today.

440
00:22:53,740 --> 00:22:54,500
What...

441
00:22:54,940 --> 00:22:56,740
Zhao Yuanhao is unbearable!

442
00:22:56,940 --> 00:22:58,340
He proclaimed himself the emperor

443
00:22:59,060 --> 00:23:01,980
and asked us to acknowledge his title

444
00:23:02,740 --> 00:23:04,620
and treat him as an independent ruler,

445
00:23:04,740 --> 00:23:06,940
or he’d wage war against us.

446
00:23:10,060 --> 00:23:11,540
All royal family members have arrived.

447
00:23:12,140 --> 00:23:13,900
This banquet can’t be canceled,

448
00:23:14,220 --> 00:23:15,260
or it’ll be seen as a bad omen

449
00:23:15,580 --> 00:23:17,100
and unsettle the guests.

450
00:23:17,620 --> 00:23:19,340
Also, it’ll boost the rebels’ morale.

451
00:23:22,820 --> 00:23:24,660
But if His Majesty refuses to see ministers

452
00:23:25,900 --> 00:23:27,780
because of the banquet,

453
00:23:28,740 --> 00:23:30,420
he’ll be considered indulging himself in pleasure.

454
00:23:42,940 --> 00:23:43,780
What are you doing?

455
00:23:47,580 --> 00:23:49,540
You’re only a servant at the Scholar Academy.

456
00:23:49,940 --> 00:23:50,900
Why are you studying so hard?

457
00:23:51,140 --> 00:23:52,220
Are you planning to top the exam

458
00:23:52,220 --> 00:23:53,460
to grace your family?

459
00:24:15,580 --> 00:24:16,460
Mother.

460
00:24:17,620 --> 00:24:18,340
Please…

461
00:24:19,180 --> 00:24:20,300
Please watch brother in heaven

462
00:24:21,540 --> 00:24:22,700
and bless him

463
00:24:23,820 --> 00:24:27,820
to live a long and smooth life.

464
00:24:40,060 --> 00:24:40,780
It’s raining.

465
00:24:41,140 --> 00:24:41,940
How come it’s raining heavily all of a sudden?

466
00:24:41,940 --> 00:24:42,820
Take everything back.

467
00:25:07,980 --> 00:25:09,180
Lantiao,

468
00:25:09,820 --> 00:25:11,820
did His Majesty praise you

469
00:25:12,060 --> 00:25:13,740
after performing my dance?

470
00:25:14,780 --> 00:25:15,900
This is my room.

471
00:25:16,500 --> 00:25:18,020
What are you doing here?

472
00:25:18,460 --> 00:25:20,060
I didn’t annoy you.

473
00:25:21,020 --> 00:25:22,180
You didn’t.

474
00:25:23,700 --> 00:25:25,260
I’m here only to laugh at you.

475
00:25:26,740 --> 00:25:28,020
Don’t push me.

476
00:25:29,100 --> 00:25:30,260
I heard

477
00:25:31,140 --> 00:25:32,180
during the banquet,

478
00:25:33,100 --> 00:25:33,980
after the guests

479
00:25:33,980 --> 00:25:35,500
toasted His Majesty,

480
00:25:35,940 --> 00:25:37,100
they drank for a while.

481
00:25:37,420 --> 00:25:38,460
Then His Majesty left

482
00:25:38,460 --> 00:25:39,540
to meet with court officials.

483
00:25:41,660 --> 00:25:43,220
Last time, he already said

484
00:25:43,820 --> 00:25:45,500
that he wanted to see my dance.

485
00:25:45,940 --> 00:25:47,220
Of course he’d wait

486
00:25:47,220 --> 00:25:49,140
for me to do it.

487
00:25:49,940 --> 00:25:51,460
He’d have no time

488
00:25:51,460 --> 00:25:52,260
for some clown.

489
00:25:55,740 --> 00:25:57,140
Or you intended

490
00:25:58,300 --> 00:25:59,820
to dance for the guests

491
00:26:00,020 --> 00:26:01,260
and some senior

492
00:26:01,260 --> 00:26:02,540
might be attracted by you.

493
00:26:07,260 --> 00:26:09,260
Even heaven isn’t on your side

494
00:26:10,100 --> 00:26:11,140
after you stole my dance

495
00:26:11,420 --> 00:26:12,660
and dress.

496
00:26:13,380 --> 00:26:14,660
Right after you left the waterside pavilion,

497
00:26:14,660 --> 00:26:15,500
rain started to pour down.

498
00:26:16,660 --> 00:26:17,500
Lantiao,

499
00:26:18,420 --> 00:26:19,500
you must’ve left

500
00:26:20,780 --> 00:26:22,380
a deep impression on all the noble guests

501
00:26:22,860 --> 00:26:24,340
with your soaking wet dance.

502
00:26:25,020 --> 00:26:25,700
You...

503
00:26:40,420 --> 00:26:41,740
I teased Lantiao.

504
00:26:42,700 --> 00:26:43,580
Scold me

505
00:26:43,780 --> 00:26:44,860
all you want.

506
00:26:45,020 --> 00:26:45,940
I’m not like her.

507
00:26:46,300 --> 00:26:47,700
Although she hates my guts,

508
00:26:48,100 --> 00:26:50,060
she always pretends to be friendly.

509
00:26:50,180 --> 00:26:50,900
Bah!

510
00:26:55,620 --> 00:26:56,340
Bihan,

511
00:27:00,300 --> 00:27:01,820
believe it or not,

512
00:27:02,700 --> 00:27:05,300
I won’t say this again.

513
00:27:10,900 --> 00:27:11,860
I spared no effort

514
00:27:13,620 --> 00:27:15,220
to help you realize your dream

515
00:27:15,620 --> 00:27:16,940
so that you could marry your love

516
00:27:17,740 --> 00:27:18,900
and enjoy a lifetime of happiness.

517
00:27:19,340 --> 00:27:20,900
until this very moment.

518
00:27:21,940 --> 00:27:22,820
Unfortunately,

519
00:27:25,500 --> 00:27:26,460
you’re doomed to fail.

520
00:27:29,620 --> 00:27:30,380
Instructor,

521
00:27:31,500 --> 00:27:32,540
what do you mean?

522
00:27:34,540 --> 00:27:35,340
The west’s revolted.

523
00:27:36,340 --> 00:27:37,820
A war may break out anytime.

524
00:27:38,660 --> 00:27:39,540
At this stage,

525
00:27:40,340 --> 00:27:42,220
there’s no way that His Majesty will risk

526
00:27:42,700 --> 00:27:44,020
being condemned

527
00:27:44,500 --> 00:27:45,700
to marry a dancer.

528
00:27:48,220 --> 00:27:49,020
You two

529
00:27:50,820 --> 00:27:51,820
aren’t meant to be.

530
00:27:58,220 --> 00:27:59,060
Listen to me,

531
00:28:01,020 --> 00:28:02,140
pull yourself together.

532
00:28:02,340 --> 00:28:03,420
Take out your wedding gown

533
00:28:04,580 --> 00:28:06,420
and prepare for your grand wedding.

534
00:28:07,140 --> 00:28:08,940
You’ll be living

535
00:28:08,940 --> 00:28:09,820
a well-off life

536
00:28:10,020 --> 00:28:12,140
with your children and grandchildren.

537
00:28:33,940 --> 00:28:35,220
How dares he!

538
00:28:36,540 --> 00:28:37,260
Your Majesty.

539
00:28:41,260 --> 00:28:42,020
Get out!

540
00:28:44,420 --> 00:28:46,100
I’m so sorry. Please punish me.

541
00:29:16,300 --> 00:29:19,060
Clean up your wound and dress it.

542
00:29:20,020 --> 00:29:20,900
Take today off.

543
00:29:22,060 --> 00:29:23,340
Cancel my breakfast.

544
00:29:24,940 --> 00:29:26,020
Don’t let anyone in.

545
00:29:48,860 --> 00:29:54,620
= Song =
= Xixia =

546
00:30:27,300 --> 00:30:29,020
I made three suits of armor

547
00:30:29,180 --> 00:30:30,580
with used ones of Zhenrong Army:

548
00:30:31,220 --> 00:30:32,980
one for the eldest son, a military genius;

549
00:30:33,460 --> 00:30:34,860
one for the seventh who’s always weak;

550
00:30:35,420 --> 00:30:36,780
the last one is for Danshu.

551
00:30:37,500 --> 00:30:38,500
The Caos,

552
00:30:38,820 --> 00:30:41,140
strong or weak, talented or not,

553
00:30:41,260 --> 00:30:42,740
men or women, must all remember

554
00:30:43,580 --> 00:30:45,020
that as long as a Cao can breathe,

555
00:30:45,740 --> 00:30:47,860
no land of Song can be lost.

556
00:30:55,220 --> 00:30:57,060
Zhao Yuanhao crowned himself in the west

557
00:30:57,580 --> 00:30:59,300
to assert independence and harassed our border.

558
00:30:59,300 --> 00:31:00,260
That’s predictable.

559
00:31:00,740 --> 00:31:01,580
But

560
00:31:01,580 --> 00:31:03,780
he threatened to wage war against us

561
00:31:03,900 --> 00:31:05,500
in the letter of credence,

562
00:31:06,100 --> 00:31:07,100
which is totally unexpected.

563
00:31:07,900 --> 00:31:09,580
It’s too sudden.

564
00:31:10,260 --> 00:31:11,060
His Majesty

565
00:31:11,820 --> 00:31:14,460
already anticipated the revolt.

566
00:31:15,420 --> 00:31:17,100
After Zhao Shanyu was killed,

567
00:31:17,540 --> 00:31:20,140
he secretly consulted Lv Yijian and the others

568
00:31:20,140 --> 00:31:21,180
about the situation.

569
00:31:21,780 --> 00:31:25,340
= Zhang Dexiang, courtesy name Xiyan =
Intelligence we’ve collected these years

570
00:31:25,900 --> 00:31:28,460
shows that the land of Tangut is too barren

571
00:31:29,020 --> 00:31:30,220
to produce enough grains

572
00:31:30,340 --> 00:31:32,260
to support their army

573
00:31:32,260 --> 00:31:33,260
to invade us,

574
00:31:33,580 --> 00:31:36,260
so they won’t provoke us in the near future.

575
00:31:37,020 --> 00:31:38,380
His Majesty is kind

576
